data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and simplicity in this 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bath Colonial home in the popular community of Washington . The kitchen boasts new cabinets and granite countertops and stainless appliances, creating a modern yet practical space for your culinary adventures.  The family room, with sliders leading to the rear deck, opens up to an expansive backyard. It's an ideal space for weekend barbecues, gardening projects, or simply unwinding in the fresh air. Generously sized bedrooms offer more than just a place to sleep. They provide adaptable spaces for your lifestyle, whether you need a home office, a hobby room, or a cozy reading nook. Venture downstairs to the basement, where the recreation room awaits. The drywall is already in place, leaving the finishing touches up to you. Imagine the possibilities – a casual hangout, a game room, or a creative studio. If you're seeking a home that offers practicality, flexibility, and room for your personal touch, schedule a showing today and envision the potential of making this your own cozy haven!  Main and 2nd floor windows and slider replaced in 2019.  HVAC upgraded and replaced in 2021
